<div class="box box--plain bg-pastel1">
<h3 style="margin-top: 10px;" class="h3-fsjoey">Get in touch&nbsp;</h3>
<p>Our <a href="https://www.confused.com/help/contact-us">contact form</a> is the quickest way to get in<br>
touch with us. But if you're having difficulty
using the form, please email us at
<a href="mailto:communications@confused.com">communications@confused.com</a>.</p>
<p>Alternatively, you can contact us in writing:</p>
<address>
Confused.com,<br>
3rd floor, Greyfriars House,<br>
Greyfriars Road,<br>
Cardiff,<br>
CF10 3AL,<br>
United Kingdom<br>
</address>
